HolySpirit README FILE

To build the game you will need next 3dparty software

1. SFML v2.0 (development snapshot 9163d04517 from Mar 14, 2012)

1.1 Development files (includes)

1.2 Libraries (static preferred)

To make CMake script automatically find these files add SMFLDIR environment path to the system, with will point to <SFML> folder:

SFMLDIR
-include
--SFML
---*.*
lib
-*.*

2. Latest MinGW (default C++ compiler) 

3. Code::Blocks IDE for building game core (default IDE)

5. CMake if you want to use another compiler/IDE for building game core

RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES:

MinGW:

1. libgcc_s_dw2-1.dll

2. libsndfile-1.dll

3. libstdc++-6.dll

4. mingwm10.dll
